features: The Hot Wheels Track 5-Pack Bundle features 3 track-themed packages of 5 toy cars that excel on and off Hot Wheels track.
Hot Wheels vehicles have inspired creative storytelling and independent exploration in generations of car lovers through push-around play.
With 3 track-themed packages, this bundle features 15 of the coolest and fastest 1:64 scale cars to speed and stunt on Hot Wheels tracks.
Hot Wheels cars have authentic decos, rolling wheels and supreme castings that are perfect for play or display.
Give each bundle of 15 cars as a gift for a birthday or holiday to kids 3 years old and older and Hot Wheels collectors who want the most comprehensive collection.
body.description: The Hot Wheels 5-Pack Track Bundle features 15 Hot Wheels vehicles known for their style and performance on the Hot Wheels track. Each of the five-packs features highlights from three different track-themed sets, all ready to race and stunt with authentic decos and precision. With multiple themed bundles available, kids and collectors will want them all. Each sold separately, subject to availability. Colors and decorations may vary.

reviews.reviewTitle: exciting and collectible toy set for both kids and Hot Wheels enthusiasts
reviews.reviewText: The Hot Wheels Track Bundle of 15 Toy Cars, consisting of three track-themed packs with five 1:64 scale vehicles each, offers an exciting and collectible toy experience for both kids and Hot Wheels enthusiasts. With its variety of vehicles and track-themed packs, it provides hours of thrilling playtime and makes for an excellent gift option.One of the standout features of this bundle is the range of vehicles included. The 15 toy cars represent a diverse selection of designs, colors, and styles, ensuring there's something for everyone's taste. From sleek sports cars to rugged off-roaders, the assortment caters to a wide range of preferences and allows for imaginative and creative play scenarios.The track-themed packs add an extra layer of excitement to the bundle. Each pack comes with five vehicles specifically designed for different track setups, enhancing the overall play experience. Whether it's racing through loops, conquering jumps, or tackling twists and turns, these vehicles are ready for action and provide endless fun when used with Hot Wheels tracks.
